      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4134"> </a>Before refitting the brake disc to the wheel, clean all contact surfaces thoroughly and smear a medium strength threadlocker
            on the threads of retaining screws (1).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4136"> </a>Operating on the left side, fit the phonic wheel (3).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4138"> </a>Tighten the fixing screws (1) of the brake disc (2) to the wheel following this sequence: 1-3-5-2-4.
         </div>
      </div>
